@sdiazb we are deploying variables and connections through ansible .... not a very elegant solution but gets the job done. We use simple python scripts and store variables and connections in ansible dictionary variables.

these scripts are not at all fancy ... and I believe i've seen a few PRs integrating this functionality into the CLI directly. But these scripts may help you in the short term.

https://gist.github.com/syvineckruyk/d2c96b418ed509a174e0e718cb62b20a

